{
  "texts": [
    "Testing decision support systems should be done both with relevant metrics 36 and with reliable vignettes that allow generalizations beyond the testing scenario.",
    "Because using unrepresentative vignettes for system testing can significantly influence the results -potentially leading to biased outcomes -only using representative vignettes and providing information on the vignettes that SAAs are tested with is particularly important.",
    "Stakeholders should specify the population they want to generalize to and use corresponding vignettes for evaluations.",
    "This study has several limitations.",
    "First, we could not obtain additional information for these cases."
  ]
}